The paper proposes a deep matrix factorization based solution for multi-view clustering, which involves techniques from machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, natural language processing, and social networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
